{"data": [{"id": "4742966", "title": "Nvidia: More Expensive But Still Positioned For Strong Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1547214730\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Nvidia (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span>), one could argue, has been the single most important stock of the past few years, both in terms of dominating sentiment and driving returns at the index level. The numbers are pretty staggering, according to one </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742966-nvidia-stock-more-expensive-but-still-positioned-for-strong-returns-reiterate-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 12:55:55"}, {"id": "4742960", "title": "Locking In Option 'Income' With AT&T", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AT&amp;T cell phone retail store. AT&amp;T is spinning off its media assets to concentrate on cell phone, mobility and high speed internet.\" data-id=\"1384839524\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Written by Nick Ackerman</em></p> <p>We had another rather successful option writing trade come to a close with AT&amp;T (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/T\" title=\"AT&amp;T Inc.\">T</a></span>) for the weekly December 6 expiration. What initially began as another round of short strangles on the name ended with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742960-locking-in-option-income-with-att", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 12:43:28"}, {"id": "4742959", "title": "With 60% Upside Potential, Okta Is A Key 2025 Cybersecurity Pick", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cyber Security Ransomware Email Phishing Encrypted Technology, Digital Information Protected Secured\" data-id=\"1420039900\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"827px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Just_Super</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Introduction &amp; Investment Thesis</span></h2> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724803-okta-stock-will-not-remain-cheap-for-long\">last wrote</a> about Okta (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKTA\" title=\"Okta, Inc.\">OKTA</a></span>) in October, where I reiterated my \u201cbuy\u201d rating, as I believed that the short-term investor pessimism had created an attractive investment opportunity in the company.</p> <p>In the post, I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742959-okta-key-2025-cybersecurity-pick-60-percent-upside-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 12:22:33"}, {"id": "4742957", "title": "MARA Holdings: A Pioneering Force In Crypto", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318198501/image_1318198501.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bitcoin Cryptocurrency concept\" data-id=\"1318198501\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318198501/image_1318198501.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318198501/image_1318198501.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318198501/image_1318198501.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080