-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With Quarter 4 of 2024 rapidly drawing to a close and the imminent arrival of Q1 2025 on the horizon, this season marks the most common time of the year for corporations to increase their dividend payout. This is done</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742955-tis-the-season-for-dividend-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 11:47:44"}, {"id": "4742954", "title": "AT&T Attempts To Convince You To Invest Again", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604361/image_1162604361.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AT&amp;T central office. AT&amp;T wrapped up its merger with WarnerMedia and now controls HBO, CNN and DirecTV\" data-id=\"1162604361\" data-type=