:44:15"}, {"id": "4742950", "title": "SPX Technologies: Running Too Hot Here", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Air conditioner technician repairing central air conditioning system with outdoor tools\" data-id=\"1437896577\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">bancha singchai</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>At the start of the year, I believed that shares of <strong>SPX Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPXC\" title=\"SPX Technologies, Inc.\">SPXC</a></span>)</strong> traded at premium valuations after a very successful M&amp;A induced transformation process.</p> <p>A $300 million deal for Ingenia Technologies marked the 14th acquisition since</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437896577/image_1437896577.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742950-spx-technologies-running-too-hot-here", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 11:03:19"}, {"id": "4742949", "title": "Block: I Am Upgrading My Outlook To Bullish", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth - US paper currency\" data-id=\"1445810148\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1034px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad